[{"id":"ec9a08e1c48a6af2cd0fc66ba3054745","from":"J. Epstein","from_email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to":"LVJET@aol.com","to_list":[{"name":"LVJET@aol.com","email":"LVJET@aol.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Re: G2 maintenance request / Weather update","date":"2008-06-16T11:15:35.000Z","formatted_date":"Jun 16, 2008","formatted_time":"11:15 AM","body":"yes\n\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: \"LVJET@aol.com\" <LVJET@aol.com>\nTo: JEEPROJECT@YAHOO.COM\nSent: Monday, June 16, 2008 12:50:54 AM\nSubject: G2 maintenance request / Weather update\n\nJeffrey,\nGulfstream:\nI need G2 for two days of routine maintenance, below floor visual. I don't feel comfortable doing this before a EU crossing, with our past track record coming out of maintenance.in case we depart for Paris.\nIf we start Monday morning we should be ready for flight Wed early morning.\nPlease advise if you would like me to start Monday?\n\u00a0\nBoeing: parking,\nHanger in Palm Beach for Boeing is $6,000 per month Jet Aviation\nGalaxy in PBI\u00a0is offering $150.00 per day ramp parking $4,500 per month\n****Newark is $120.00 per day ramp, $3,600.00 per month*****\naircraft is located in Cecil Field outside of Jacksonville FL.\n(Paint job for Boeing cost $158,000.00 FYI)\nplease advise your choice ?\n\u00a0\nZorro Weather is PERFECT 90 degrees high sunshine / lows 56 degrees in the evening.\nParis is OK, afternoon showers 73 degrees / 54 degrees eveing\nStanley, NM    \n\u00a0 \nTonight\nJun 15\n\nMostly Clear\nN/A\n57\u00b0\n0%\n\u00a0 \nHigh not valid after 2pm\nMon\nJun 16\n\nMostly Sunny\n92\u00b0\n57\u00b0\n10%\n\u00a0 \n92\u00b0F\nTue\nJun 17\n\nMostly Sunny\n92\u00b0\n56\u00b0\n10%\n\u00a0 \n92\u00b0F\nWed\nJun 18\n\nMostly Sunny\n90\u00b0\n56\u00b0\n10%\n\u00a0 \n90\u00b0F\nThu\nJun 19\n\nSunny\n92\u00b0\n54\u00b0\n20%\n\u00a0 \n92\u00b0F\nFri\nJun 20\n\nSunny\n91\u00b0\n53\u00b0\n10%\n\u00a0 \n91\u00b0F\nSat\nJun 21\n\nSunny\n91\u00b0\n54\u00b0\n10%\n\u00a0 \n91\u00b0F\nSun\nJun 22\n\nSunny\n91\u00